thread.title: Patricia

author: Patricia
title: Patricia
text: We ordered Senna Plus, the Plus is an added stool softener. We were sent plain Senna. I called a month ago and spoke with David and he said he would call me back. Then last week after a month we called back and spoke with Cheyenne and she said she would call me back the next day with a resolution to this problem, still no return call! I would not recommend doing business with this company as if you are sent a cheaper and or incorrect product than what you ordered they do not correct their mistakes!
